 2020-10022020-12-07,  ,  ,  ,  GAC
ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectTrade Continuity between Canada and the United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland **Agreement**
PrecisOrder authorizing the Prime Minister or the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, or the Minister of Foreign Affairs to delegate authority to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the AGREEMENT ON TRADE CONTINUITY BETWEEN CANADA AND THE UNITED KINGDOM OF GREAT BRITAIN AND NORTHERN IRELAND, and related binding instruments.
